Package: manders1D
Type: Package
Title: Compute Mander's Co-Localization Coefficient along One Dimension
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alexis Weinreb
Maintainer: Alexis Weinreb <alexis.weinreb@yale.edu>
Description: Given two channels (from fluorescence microscopy), use one channel for
    thresholding and define "domains", then evaluate the intensity of the second channel
    within the domains.
